{"tid":44681,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[駕駛台]HKGDC駕駛台 (9)  我地已經提早過聖誕啦～","createTime":"2016-12-18T12:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T20:07:09.000Z","uid":32150,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59495de7cd277aaad5b070969e2ab5e682370e9a","tid":44681,"uid":32150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"[駕駛台]HKGDC駕駛台 (9)  我地已經提早過聖誕啦～<br />\n<br />\n本台主要為集結一眾愛車之人，不時聚會交流愛車近況！<br />\n<br />\n現在此宣布，經過長時間既招募人數開始壯大<br />\n一輪討論製作後HKGDC 既會章亦已經順利完成！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/096U9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F096U9S.jpg&h=239b049f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車會貼一套兩張：<br />\n1. 有車圖案HKGDC玻璃靜電貼<br />\n2. 亮面HKGDC淨字車身貼紙<br />\n<br />\n3. 啞面HKGDC淨字車身貼紙 (限量附送)<br />\n初期加入特送上無再版既&quot;啞面HKGDC淨字車身貼紙&quot;乙張<br />\n<br />\n曾經出席大聚並已有會貼即可享有各種車會會員優惠(e.g. Coating，Warp車，車Cam，音響，etc...)<br />\n其他會員福利將會慢慢增加！<br />\n<br />\n更新福利：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7t10den.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7t10den.jpg&h=4d97afa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地會有自家櫈啦～大家出聚唔洗再企得咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外HKGDC 油咭終於推出！！<br />\nHKGDC油咭可以有Shell/Esso 比各位自行選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nShell/Esso 只可二揀一：<br />\nShell -$2.30/L<br />\nEsso -$2.20/L<br />\n<br />\n豐富聚會經驗，亦歡迎新朋友加入，令本會氣氛更加熱鬧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日既十二月大聚，大家仲交換禮物<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/205030_32e1ac3c76501ae4488099d4f656152f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F205030_32e1ac3c76501ae4488099d4f656152f.jpg&h=99ff9117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直不定期有車聚，內容多為洗車/影車/食糖水/遊車河<br />\n並定期舉行大型活動，例如全谷同行燒烤等等<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打只要有牌有車～無任歡迎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入Gp既留名後用QR Add我啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/24/203742_296ec803e3477b689acdc016f8aaf1a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F24%2F203742_296ec803e3477b689acdc016f8aaf1a0.jpg&h=ac5f4943&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7d76edfa545871ee9110647de3f5af9c040f020","tid":44681,"uid":20581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"留名 開心V power"},{"pid":"59e5cb4c2aee766a88ff247019e47f2c525850e8","tid":44681,"uid":66525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"黎明"},{"pid":"87c780f8107cc4492cab0f9c43adc8e0dff57539","tid":44681,"uid":13796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"留個名先， 是咪乜車都比玩？"},{"pid":"9ccf13f14ecb2ce439f66c5fc79cd6a2baf27f96","tid":44681,"uid":20581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:25:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留個名先， 是咪乜車都比玩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇話比唔比玩<br />\n想玩就可以一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f8584168f7b13deb473308dc09a80b896f1615","tid":44681,"uid":24481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留個名先， 是咪乜車都比玩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個group可以話係認人唔認車 啱傾啱玩就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608b7f90a7f9acd75bdf7d5065d1e52bbff4d76f","tid":44681,"uid":54942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"happy corner<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94761746d935b210894a6187947519418346660","tid":44681,"uid":12662,"lik